---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Nope"
  description="A bit about us."
  enableClientRouter={true}
>
  <section class="about-shell layout-shell page-shell">
    <div class="about-grid layout-grid">
      <article class="about">

        <p class="p--intro">
          nope studio is a small web agency based just outside Stockholm, Sweden. We build websites, apps, and digital things that capture the soul of the people and companies behind them. No generic slop. Just clean, minimal, human-made work.
        </p>

        <p class="p--punch">
          The name is<br>intentional.
        </p>

        <p class="p--body p--tilt-left">
          I say no to most things. Not out of stubbornness. Out of conviction. Most things don't need to exist... extra features nobody asked for, pages that fill space, design that decorates instead of communicates.
        </p>

        <p class="p--body p--right">
          I try to remove all of it. <em>What's left is usually better.</em>
        </p>

        <p class="p--display">
          method,<br>not<br>aesthetic (kinda).
        </p>

        <p class="p--body p--tilt-right">
          Every decision starts with a question: Does this need to be here? If the answer isn't clearly yes, it goes. I apply this to everything. The work I take on, the words I write, the pixels I place.
        </p>

        <p class="p--punch p--center">
          Good design<br>disappears.
        </p>

        <p class="p--body">
          The typeface, the spacing, the colour, the weight of a line ___ these are all decisions. Decisions made carelessly produce work that feels wrong even when people can't say why. I try to make them carefully.
        </p>

        <p class="p--outro">
          The name wasn't a strategy.<br>It was just the <strong>first honest thing</strong>.
        </p>

      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
  }

  .about {
    grid-column: 3 / 11;
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem) clamp(6rem, 14vw, 12rem);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    overflow-x: hidden;
    transition: background 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .about p {
    font-family: var(--font-family-prose);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about .p--intro {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 52ch;
    margin-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
  }

  .about .p--punch {
    font-family: var(--font-family-base);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    max-width: 18ch;
    margin-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
  }

  .about .p--body {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 48ch;
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .about .p--right {
    margin-inline-start: auto;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .about .p--display {
    font-family: var(--font-family-base);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 12vw, 10rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-black);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-block: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
  }

  .about .p--center {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .about .p--outro {
    font-family: var(--font-family-base);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-top: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
  }

  .about .p--tilt-left {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 44ch;
    transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .about .p--tilt-right {
    transform: rotate(1deg);
  }

  /* Experimental theme */
  :global([data-theme="experimental"]) .about {
    color: var(--brand-green);
  }

  :global([data-theme="experimental"]) .about p {
    color: var(--brand-green);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
  }
</style>
